    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-divider guten-element guten-divider guten-jBXkeU\"><div class=\"guten-divider-wrapper\"><div class=\"guten-divider-default guten-divider-line guten-divider-regular\"></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"9YZccd\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-9YZccd layout-boxed align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-top\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-bottom\"></div><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-lBvXW9\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"sticky-wrapper\" data-id=\"lBvXW9\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\">\n<p>Shimon Alroy Ben Shitrit was born on April 21, 2003, in Beit She&#8217;an, Israel, as the fourth child of Iris and Raphael Ben Shitrit. Growing up in a loving household with his siblings Oria, Yahel, Naora, and Leah, Alroy was cherished by his family and known for his curiosity and adventurous spirit. He shared a particularly close bond with his sister Yahel, who worked as a nurse. She often described him as having a &#8220;heart of gold,&#8221; always caring for others with warmth and kindness.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Inspired by tales of heroism from his family and community, Alroy joined the Israeli Defense Forces (IDF) after graduating high school. On March 29, 2022, he enlisted in the IDF&#8217;s Combat Intelligence Collection Corps as a balloon surveillance operator, a role that demanded vigilance and bravery. Alroy quickly earned the respect of his peers and superiors, recognized for his leadership skills and calm demeanor under pressure.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ben Shitrit family was immensely proud of Alroy&#8217;s service. His father, Raphael, a former mayor of Beit She&#8217;an, frequently spoke of Alroy\u2019s dedication and bravery. However, on October 7, 2023, tragedy struck during a battle at Nahal Oz, where Alroy&#8217;s unit faced a fierce assault by Hamas militants. Alroy fought bravely but tragically lost his life, leaving his family and community devastated.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The news of Alroy\u2019s passing was a tremendous blow to Beit She&#8217;an. Thousands of residents gathered to mourn the loss of a young man who had become a symbol of hope and courage. His cousin, Liraz Sharvit, captured the community&#8217;s grief by describing Alroy as an &#8220;angel&#8221; whose smile lit up lives and whose kind heart touched many.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In response to this tragedy, Alroy&#8217;s father Raphael became an advocate for justice, joining a Civil Investigation Committee to uncover the truth behind the events of October 7th. He called for accountability, demanding a state investigation to prevent such tragedies from occurring in the future.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To honor Alroy&#8217;s memory, the Ben Shitrit family shared stories of his kindness and bravery, ensuring his legacy would live on. They even shared his favorite dish, beet kibbeh, as a reminder of the joyful moments they cherished together.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alroy was posthumously promoted to First Sergeant, a recognition of his courage and dedication. As he was laid to rest in the military section of Beit She&#8217;an Cemetery, the community bid farewell to a young hero who had given everything for his country.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Though Alroy&#8217;s life was tragically short, his legacy continues to inspire those who knew him. His story serves as a poignant reminder of the courage and sacrifice of IDF soldiers and the enduring spirit of those who dedicate their lives to protecting their nation. The Ben Shitrit family remains determined to honor Alroy&#8217;s memory, ensuring his spirit will live on in the hearts of all who loved him.</p>\n</div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-1Xd8RO\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"sticky-wrapper\" data-id=\"1Xd8RO\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"uxLb9c\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-uxLb9c layout-fullwidth align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-top\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-bottom\"></div><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-BcvNAD\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"sticky-wrapper\" data-id=\"BcvNAD\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"D1RzGC\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-D1RzGC layout-boxed align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-top\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-bottom\"></div><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-E9m9gW\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"sticky-wrapper\" data-id=\"E9m9gW\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-image guten-element guten-image guten-bLjj9P\"><a class=\"guten-image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"gutenverse-image-box-filled\" src=\"https://iron-swords.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/candle.png\" height=\"3558\" width=\"1192\"/></a></div>\n</div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-VBiLav\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"sticky-wrapper\" data-id=\"VBiLav\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-XIlfJ6\">First Name</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-9MST9I\">Shimon Alroy</h5>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-rbIszp\">Last Name</h4>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-0y9ag8\">&nbsp;Ben Shitrit</h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-IDcGkf\">Age</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-Nu61ku\">20</h5>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-fbm6aB\">Fell On</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-oiInFM\">07 OCTOBER 2023</h5>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-wePmlX\">Army Unit</h4>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-Ukrykc\"><a href=\"https://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%97%D7%99%D7%9C_%D7%94%D7%92%D7%A0%D7%AA_%D7%94%D7%92%D7%91%D7%95%D7%9C%D7%95%D7%AA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Combat Intelligence Collection Corps</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-2D7lb5\">Army Rank</h4>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-NbiMeg\">Staff sergeant</h2>\n</div></div></div>\n</div></section></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-rhvrRc\">\u05d9\u05d4\u05d9 \u05d6\u05db\u05e8\u05d5 \u05d1\u05e8\u05d5\u05da</h2>\n</div></div></div>\n</div></section></div>\n\n\n</div></div></div>\n</div></section></div>\n",
